\id TIT - Zyphe
\h TITAS
\toc1 TITAS KHATEI PAUL CAKUA
\toc2 TITAS
\toc3 Tit
\mt1 TITAS
\mt2 KHATEI PAUL CAKUA
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Khazing sae le Zisu Khri apostol a cangpaw kama Paul tah kaa hrongpaw peh zingnah chungletah ka sawtei hmuisui a cangpaw Tita khatah ca ka ca kua. Khazing tah a thingpaw sahlo khah Khazing tlechainah lang langhme a chuinah a cangpaw aa zingnah le biadih hninah letah aa changchy nápawtah kama cawh tawpaw ka cang.
\v 2 Ma zingnah le hninah cawh chaizaw hringnah hnabeisuinah letah a pahnia ka, ma cawh Khazing a hing thai lypaw taco cai hrangtho hlai taitah bia a kang ciapaw a cang.
\v 3 Ama tah a cai a zaw a tah tihtah a bia khah phungreiná khei palang sá pawtah kaa Pachahtu Khazing a biapehnah thong tah rai a pa khing.
\p 
\v 4 Paw Khazing le a ma Pachahtu Khri Zisu taiteipaw ningdonah le thlawlungnah cawh nama khatah ung ky seh.
\s1 Krit tuiraw letah Tita a hre ruapaw rai
\p 
\v 5 Krit tuiraw letei ka ca chiasipaw cawh ka ca chingsipaw hrakhei rai paling lypaw sahlo khah paling rua pawtah le khua maikaw lekhei khrisaw macang sahlo rawh pah lai rua pawtah a cang.
\v 6 Khrisaw macang cawh suise a kawh lypaw, nupui pakheh suitei a hnuipaw, a sawtei leh Khazing a zingpaw he le piathynah le bia nge lynah lang letah thaichianah a hnui lypaw cang he seh.
\v 7 Khrisaw hotu cawh Khazing rai a mingkaitu a cangnah cawtah suise a kawh lypaw, a palai a patui lypaw, a thing a paching lypaw, zu rui ahmang lypaw, a piathy lypaw, ahmang lypaw a miasangnah a du lypaw,
\v 8 ma hlui co pasungpanaw a thaipaw, chahnah a dupaw, pungsaw dunah a tlepakhih khypaw, mehding a cangpaw, hringzia a pathaipaw le a dih teitah a ungpaw cang seh.
\v 9 Ama aa cawngpahpaw thawngchawbia, biadih khah cyky tah a zingpaw a cang a. Taico minghringpaw khah a hmangpaw cawngpahnah khei thawzaang pei khy a he ka, cawngpahnah aa cakhaepaw sahlo khah aa paanah khah a palang khy a.
\p 
\v 10 Zecawtamaw tatah male dy a hmangpaw, bia rei a hawngpaw le, dungkhei a hmangpaw mehlupui a ung he. A hlu vy cawh cingpa a taipaw phu a cang cai he.
\v 11 Ma sahlo cawh aa kaw pamai a hy, zecawtamaw tatah cawngpah ly ruapaw aa cawngpahnah pawhe takhei ingchungkho ialia tah hna aa hnawhsah thlu he. A miasang du tah ma hrahei aa cawngpah laipaw he a cang.
\v 12 Aaning aa khuavang a cangpaw lilaw takhei hmai, “Krit tuiraw cawngsaw sahlo cawh hing paria he ka, saraang hapaw, mehthawthi le mehzawng a cang he,” tatah a tah kho.
\v 13 A reipaw cawh ahmangpaw a cang. Macawtaco a sah pui tah raw my lo, ma pawsui co zingnah letah a biatah khy he ka,
\v 14 Juda aa phung a reilaipaw le biahmuisui a hlawhpaw cawngsaw sahlo naw aa pehpaw he bia khah nawthlia pah lytah aa ung a.
\v 15 Mehpathaipaw caw taco zehmai heh a pathai thlu thlang. Canghrasala mehpialui le Khazing a zing lypaw aa caw taco aa thinglung chiachaw thluidangnah a pialuinah cawtah a pathaipaw zehmai ung be.
\v 16 Khazing kaa hni tah he ka, canghrasala aa tuasaná tah aa hlawh. Aaning sahlo cawh du a chui lypaw, rei a nge lypaw, hmingchaw a tua ruapaw tei a tlah lypaw a cang he.
\c 2
\s1 Ahmangpaw cawngpahnah
\p 
\v 1 Nama tu taco cawngpahnah ahmangpaw khatei a tlahpaw khah cawngpah my lo.
\v 2 Macangpaw sahlo cawh singvang teitah le zawchuipaw tah ung pawtah le ma leh ma a tlepakhih khypaw cang pawtah le zingnah ahmangpaw le donah le ingkhynah hnui pawtah cawngpah my lo.
\p 
\v 3 Ma hraco canu macang sahlo khah aa hringzia letah Khazing a cizaw thaipaw, cawngui a thai lypaw, zu a rang lypaw, hmingchaw tua cawngpah a thaipaw naa cang ruapaw a cang tatah cawngpah my lo.
\v 4 Mataico aaning taco a kung a ny vypaw canu khah aa pasae leh le aa sawtei leh a dopaw,
\v 5 ma leh ma a tlepakhih khypaw, a pathaipaw, ingchungkho tungtuh a thaipaw, mehchaw le pasae rei a ngepaw aa cang pawtah aa cawngpah khy he. Ma pawsui co ahotahmai tah Khazing bia khah reipachia khy bei he.
\p 
\v 6 Ma hraco capaw mehny sahlo khah ma leh ma a tlepakhih khypaw aa cang nápawtah pasy my lo.
\v 7 Zezongpui letah hmingchaw tuaná khei a mingpai tlang pawtah ung my lo. Na cawngpahnah lekhei dingnah le biatahnah le
\v 8 biarei thangrei letah suise a kawh lypaw tah ung la, ma hratei na tua caco a ca dytu sahlo khah aa ning a ze a, zecawtamaw tatah kaaning letah reipachia ruapaw zehmai hmuh a bei he.
\p 
\v 9 Sae sahlo khah zezongpui letah naa bui leh reinge la, aa bia ei khe la, aa lungtong a zawng my lo,
\v 10 aa hming zong ruh pah khe la, zingchui tlang naa cangnah cawh hmingchaw tuaná khei palang hri my lo, tatah cawngpah my lo. Ma pawsui co, a ma Pachahtu Khazing kong cawngpahnah khah tlechai tlang a chuipaw a cangnah zia kawting tah a lang a.
\p 
\v 11 Zecawtamaw tatah pachahnah a chuakhuipaw Khazing ningdonah cawh ming vytei khatah a lang myca.
\v 12 Ma ningdonah taco Khazing zetah reilynah le ngaisaw sua dunah sahlo hlawh rua pawtah a ma cawngpah. Ma leh ma a tlepakhih khypaw, mehding cang pawtah le Khazing cizaw hmo teitah atocai lehei ung rua paw takhei a ma pasy.
\v 13 Alaisuipaw kaa Khazing le Pachahtu a cangpaw Zisu Khri rungnaw pawtah a paly nápaw khah hnabeisuinah alaisuipaw kaa haw thlang chung lehei ma hraco kaa ung ruapaw a cang.
\v 14 Ama cawh kaaning vytei khah chahlynah vytei taitah tlang rua pawtah le Ama a tei cang rua pawtah le pathaisá pawtah le hmingchaw tua dunah hnui rua pawtah kaa cawtah a hringnah a peipaw a cang.
\p 
\v 15 Ma sahlo heh na cawngpah ruapaw he cawh a cang hi. Nawhnuinah chitah aaning sahlo cawh pasy la, chinghring my lo. Ahotahmai tah ca zongte kheh he seh.
\c 3
\s1 Hmingchaw tuanah
\p 
\v 1 Uhtu sahlo le naw hnuitu sahlo khah cizaw la, aa bia nge la, hmingchaw tua rua pawtah a maipacia my lo,
\v 2 ahohmai reipachia khe lo, de teitah ung la, zawngrawhnah le a panynah khah, mingting cung letah a langsah my lo, tatah cawngsaw sahlo khah na cawngpah kaw he a.
\p 
\v 3 Khuahlai ning taco kaaning sahlo zong heh mehruh le, reingenah a hnui lypaw le, dungkhei tah a ungpaw le a nawngsenah phingzakih sae a cang ciapaw longtei ka cang he peh. Ziahnuinah le hnachuanah khatei a za hringpaw ka cang peh. Male a hua he peh ka, kaaning zong aa ma hua hrah he.
\v 4 Canghrasala kaa Khazing le Pachahtu donah le chahnah a lang tihtah,
\v 5 a ma pachah. A dingpaw hming kaa tuanah cawtah cang lytah ama zawngenah rawng tah a cang hri. Thlawpaw Pathai pathanah le sipathainah thongtah a ma pachahpaw a cang.
\v 6 Ma cawh kaa Pachahtu Zisu Khri thongtah a Thlawpaw Pathai cawh a hlupui tah a ma luiso.
\v 7 A ningdonah thong khei thaicangsah cang peh ka, chaizaw hringnah hnabeisuinah ry a cytu kaa cang khy hrah peh.
\v 8 Ma heh zing tlang a tlahpaw bia a cang. Macawtaco ma hming sahlo heh na calia lai rua pawtah ka dupaw a cang. Ma pawsui co, Khazing letei angepainah a pahniapaw sahlo he tah hmingchaw tuanah kong letah tua ceingei pawtah a peh khynah aa hnui a. Ma hming sahlo heh ming maikaw cawtah a chawpaw le a chahnaipaw a cang.
\p 
\v 9 Canghrasala hruchuipaw bia a eilainah le pathlahtu sahlo ming cadai lai tei a eichaenah le phungbia kong letei a hry a chaenah tahpaw vytei sahlo heh cahri my lo. Zecawtamaw tatah a chahnai lypaw, zehmai a cang lypaw a cang.
\v 10 A chaichynah a chuakhuipaw cawh uikheh uihning raeringnah na peh khy taico, ama khaco zehmai tua khawh kheh.
\v 11 Ma hapaw cawngsaw cawh a rawhnah ahmang lypaw le a suapaw, ama le ama thaily a cangsahpaw a cang takhah hnih my lo.
\s1 A changnah biacawnah
\p 
\v 12 Artema maw a cang ly leh Taikhika maw ka va thlaw tih he tah Nekapoli lang kama kha a vong pawtah a zawng my lo, zecawtamaw tatah ma leco thlasih chung vytei ung ka pachia.
\v 13 Sihni a cangpaw Zena le Apolo khah aa khuatlongnah letah baw la, zezong aa hiapaw na tua khypaw maikaw khah tuapah my lo.
\v 14 Kaa cawngsaw sahlo takhei hmingchaw tuanah kong letah aa cawng hrahring rua pawtah le ung cakhawng thlang lytah ningting cawtah a hiapaw e le ba chuakhui khah a zawng cypaw a cang tahpaw khah aa hni a hia.
\p 
\v 15 Kama kha a ungpaw vytei tah a dang pawtah aa ca tah he. Zingnah letei a ma dopaw sahlo he khah a dang pawtah pa tah pah my lo.
\p Khazing ningdonah cawh naa zongmingtei cung letah ung ky seh.
